EmailTemplate.name: Host Application Reviewed - External India
EmailTemplate.subject: Thank you for Submitting a Climate Corps Host Application
EmailTemplate.textOnly:
Dear {!Host_Application__c.Respondent_Name__c},
With your Climate Corps fellow/s now confirmed, I am thrilled to officially welcome you to Climate Corps! We’re delighted to have you onboard and look forward to an exciting and productive summer. The attached “2023 Welcome to Climate Corps” file contains helpful information and a timeline to keep handy as we make preparations for these fellowships. Please review it at your convenience.
We are following up with your fellow/s for program orientation and to get them on the pathway to Fellow Training, which will take place on May 8-12 on Zoom. You can also expect to hear from your fellow/s again soon to further build their workplan (suggested template attached) and finalize start and end dates.
Together with my team at EDF, I will be providing Engagement Management services to the fellows throughout the summer. That includes offering guidance throughout their fellowship experience, advising on questions you or they may have, and helping to connect the fellows with resources and information as needed throughout the project. The most immediate next steps at this stage are to:
Finalize start and end dates Work with your fellow on developing their workplan (template attached) Sign the attached host agreement and reply to me (if you did not submit a host application beforehand) Connect with me and your fellow for a kick-off call to ensure everyone is aligned and ready to go for the project. I will be following up to schedule that sometime during the two weeks prior to the fellowship start date. Complete any HR onboarding formalities before the start of the fellowship to get the fellow up and running from the first week, including gathering any data they'll need for the projects, setting up introductory meetings with important stakeholders, etc.
Thank you again. Please do not hesitate to reach out to me (pmishra@edf.org) if you have any questions.
Best,
Paridhi Mishra
Project Advisor, Climate Corps India
